{
  "texts": [
    "As noted by Wei et al. (2022a), training LLMs using a prompt packed with query-related information can yield substantial performance enhancement.",
    "Users can ask questions in the chat box by typing or using voice input.",
    "The response is displayed at the top of the page, and the document chunks used for the answer can be checked at the bottom (see Figure 2).",
    "The tool was constructed utilizing two innovative technologies-Gradio and LlamaIndex.",
    "Gradio, a tool developed by Abid et al. (2019), serves as the backbone for both our front and back ends."
  ]
}